OL,3,CMeet the quirky singer serenading
OL,4,Cshoppers from her piano bike
OL,6,FA quirky singer is livening up town
OL,7,Fcentres and festivals around the West
OL,8,FCountry with her music performed on a
OL,9,F"piano bike".
OL,11,FChloe Marie Aston, 20, from Ilfracombe
OL,12,Fpicked up the instrument for the first
OL,13,Ftime five years ago and has been
OL,14,Fserenading shoppers ever since.
OL,16,FNow, as festival season draws to a
OL,17,Fclose, she sat down with ITV News West
OL,18,FCountry to reflect on her career so
OL,19,Ffar and plans for the future.
