OL,3,CMeet the quirky singer serenading
OL,4,Cshoppers from her piano bike
OL,6,FChloe said: "It's such a nice job to
OL,7,Fhave, to go out and play music and
OL,8,Fmake people happy.
OL,10,F"But it's weird to be kind of a known
OL,11,Ffigure in the South West now."
OL,13,FUntil this summer, Chloe helped out in
OL,14,Fher family's petrol station, which
OL,15,Fthey'd owned for roughly 40 years.
OL,17,FWhen her grandad sold it in July, she
OL,18,Fmade the leap to busking full-time and
OL,19,Fplans to continue through the winter.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
