OL,3,CMeet the quirky singer serenading
OL,4,Cshoppers from her piano bike
OL,6,F"I will probably do shorter days with
OL,7,Flots of breaks for hot chocolate, but
OL,8,FI have some fingerless gloves and last
OL,9,Fyear I invested in an electric hand
OL,10,Fwarmer, so I'm well prepared," Chloe
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FAlthough she's now fully fitted-out
OL,14,Fwith everything she needs, Chloe's
OL,15,Fpiano bike hasn't always been part of
OL,16,Fher act.
OL,18,F"I started busking when I was 14 and
OL,19,Fback then I played the guitar. But I
OL,20,Fwasn't very good at it and I used to
OL,21,Fcomplain about it.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
