OL,3,CMeet the quirky singer serenading
OL,4,Cshoppers from her piano bike
OL,6,F"My dad would sit there, watching me
OL,7,Fplay, and then one day he came up with
OL,8,Fthe idea of putting a piano on a bike.
OL,10,F"I didn't know how to play the piano
OL,11,Fat all at the time, so he told me his
OL,12,Fidea and he said, 'If I build this
OL,13,Fpiano bike, will you learn to play the
OL,14,Fpiano?' and so I did.
OL,16,F"A lot of people think I'm selling ice
OL,17,Fcream and then I cycle past and they
OL,18,Fsee the keys and realise 'oh it's a
OL,19,Fpiano'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
