OL,3,CMeet the quirky singer serenading
OL,4,Cshoppers from her piano bike
OL,6,F"People often say 'I can't believe it,
OL,7,Fthat's so weird'
OL,9,F"Now I've been doing it for five
OL,10,Fyears, when I revisit places people
OL,11,Fsay 'oh look, that's Chloe'."
OL,13,FThis summer she's travelled to fairs
OL,14,Fand towns across the region, from
OL,15,FLaunceston to the Melplash Show, in
OL,16,FSomerset.
OL,18,FChloe said her influences include the
OL,19,FNorwegian singer Sigrid, and British
OL,20,Findie rock band The Last Dinner Party.
